    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >点击上图可加入我们的Discord频道。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也欢迎加入我们的官方QQ群：879331938</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306980/extras/6daa4738e36783937b0be8ce8b84ea24.apng?t=1741346132\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306980/extras/6daa4738e36783937b0be8ce8b84ea24.poster.avif?t=1741346132\" class=\"bb_img\" width=620 height=124 /></picture></span>「Replik Survivors」是一款具有角色扮演和轻度肉鸽元素的时间生存游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中，你将扮演一名Replik (克隆体)，去打败实验中出现的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306980/extras/80e4f6bbc5a83cd34c6372de1abc4a0d.poster.avif?t=1741346132\" width=620 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306980/extras/80e4f6bbc5a83cd34c6372de1abc4a0d.webm?t=1741346132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>在这款游戏中你可以利用强化系统强化自身属性，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还可以自由构建各种攻击触发器，配置顺序，创造属于自己的攻击组合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，还有多个不同的角色等着你去发现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・ 多种攻击方式和强化属性可供选择</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・ 7 位完全不同玩法的角色</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・ 5 个难度级别，不同的敌人，不同的首领</p>",
